description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 3:

Twitter-banned Alex Berenson on all the latest covid data the media won't tell you about. Virginia election: Youngkin vs. McAuliffe. C&B review the Chappelle Netflix special. Five For Fighting's John Ondrasik on his Afghanistan protest song: "Blood on My Hands."
